# Regenerate the hero demo:  vhs scripts/hero.tape
# Then optimize:  gifsicle -O3 --lossy=80 --colors 96 docs/assets/hamzaish-hero.gif -o /tmp/o.gif && mv /tmp/o.gif docs/assets/hamzaish-hero.gif
# v1 "factory in motion" — real command output. Replace with a live idea->scaffold->ship TUI recording when ready.
Output "docs/assets/hamzaish-hero.gif"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1100
Set Height 560
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 24
Set TypingSpeed 38ms
Hide
Type "clear" Enter
Show
Sleep 400ms
Type "# Builder Mode: an AI-native startup factory that doesn't stop at code"
Enter
Sleep 1300ms
Type "bun run eval --no-llm        # the agent-blind judge: real verdicts, not vibes"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 4200ms
Type "bun run check-changelog      # honesty guard: every shipped feature documented"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 3500ms
Type "# 32 agents - 128 practices - 39 playbooks - a brain that remembers"
Enter
Sleep 1300ms
Type "# Claude Code, Cursor, Codex, Windsurf. point your agent here, then build."
Enter
Sleep 2400ms
